Package: ardesia
Architecture: any
Depends:  libatk1.0-0 (>= 1.9.0), libc6 (>= 2.3.4-1), libcairo2 (>= 1.0.2), libfontconfig1 (>= 2.3.0), libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.8.0), libgtk2.0-0 (>= 2.8.0), libpango1.0-0 (>= 1.10.1), libx11-6, libxcursor1 (>> 1.1.2), libxext6, libxfixes3, libxi6, libxinerama1, libxrandr2, libxrender1, libgsl0ldbl, recordmydesktop
Description: Gtk interface to make annotations on the screen.
 Ardesia enables you to make coloured free-hand annotations on your screen and record it.
 .
 This is especially useful when making presentations, to highlight
 things or point out things of interest.
 .
 Ardesia is XInput-Aware, so if you have a graphic tablet or a whiteboard
 you can draw lines with different strength, select color, erase things, etc.

